formatted_address: 469 Bukit Batok West Ave 9, #01-18 West Hawker Centre, Singapore 650469
name: Urfan's Rojak & Prata Paradise

reviews.text: Got egg, cheese and normal prata, at $2, $2.5, $1.3 respectively. Chocolate tissue plata was $4. All were pretty average, I think they could do with more cheese/ egg added.

Premade lousy awful prata.. requested one more plate as the kids were sharing, and was being question “why you need 1 more plate?”

The hell? This is the first time we were being question like this and obviously we need it?!

It’s not them washing anyway, why ask so much?!

Will not be ordering from them again, not recommended.

vicinity: 469 Bukit Batok West Avenue 9, #01-18 West Hawker Centre
